big hole" She grinned, and fired it point blank between his eyes, 
before brining up her laser gun and pointing it straight at the back 
of his head.

"Committed a crime? What's the matter with you?" Teltoli said 
sarcastically. "She's living her life, which by the way, is none of 
your business"
